  "exploreItemMinimalistPandaPrompt": "A tiny minimalist  tattoo of a cute panda sitting upright, facing slightly right, drawn with clean black lines and soft micro-shading. The panda holds a thin green stem with small purple lavender flowers, with subtle botanical detail and glossy black ears and arms. The design is centered on ankle skin, photographed in natural light with shallow depth of field and a minimal, professional tattoo reference style in a 1:1 composition.",
